sql:
SELECT county_id, AVG(avg_trip_length) AS average_trip_length
FROM mobility_summary
GROUP BY county_id;

SELECT avg_trip_length AS average_trip_length
FROM mobility_summary
WHERE county_id = 1234;

external_knowledge:
Short trips refer to trips between 1 and 3 miles; The average trip lengths are calculated based on predefined distance ranges and their corresponding average distances.

- Trips less than 1 mile are assumed to be 0 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 1 and 3 miles are assumed to be 2 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 3 and 5 miles are assumed to be 4 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 5 and 10 miles are assumed to be 7.5 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 10 and 25 miles are assumed to be 17.5 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 25 and 50 miles are assumed to be 37.5 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 50 and 100 miles are assumed to be 75 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 100 and 250 miles are assumed to be 175 miles for average calculation;
- Trips between 250 and 500 miles are assumed to be 375 miles for average calculation;
- Trips greater than or equal to 500 miles are assumed to be 500 miles for average calculation.

